aboutEyebrow: About Live Fire Instruction
aboutTitle: Developing safe and responsible shooters
aboutDescription: >-
  Since 2016, Live Fire Instruction has served as Northern Virginia's premier
  destination for expert-led firearms safety and proficiency training.
  Headquartered in Fairfax and utilizing the NRA National Range (the world's
  most advanced indoor shooting facility), our team of NRA-certified
  instructors specializes in teaching first-time shooters and individuals
  seeking a Virginia Concealed Carry Permit (CCW). Our mission is to transform
  novice shooters into safe, confident, and responsible firearm owners through a
  curriculum that prioritizes safety fundamentals, ethics, and hands-on skill
  development. We take pride in our 98% pass rate for CCW qualifications and
  have successfully trained over 7,500 students across NoVA, Washington D.C.,
  and Maryland. By providing all necessary materials and firearms, we offer a
  comprehensive, low-pressure gateway to responsible self-protection in the
  Northern Virginia area.
reasons:
  - NRA Certified Instructors with extensive teaching experience
